#: base/services/update_check.py:85
msgid ""
"Hi!\n"
"\n"
"An update is available for your eventyay installation.\n"
"Please check out eventyay.com for more information.\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"Your eventyay team"
msgstr ""
"Ahoj!\n"
"\n"
"Pro vaši instalaci eventyay je k dispozici aktualizace.\n"
"Další informace najdete na eventyay.com.\n"
"S pozdravem,\n"
"Tým eventyay"

